        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>Imagine your life in 10 years time. What will it look like?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 60 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>I don't know... it's quite hard to imagine what my life would look like in 10 years. Maybe i'm gonna be a famous comuter scientist, who is the author of somes famous piece of software, maybe a virus .... I've always been fascinated by the way botnets where working. That much power in the hands of one (or a few) man. the biggest are controlling millions of computers and are still anonymous, they're just genius.</p>
            </div>
